Please refer to the online documentation at www.asymptopia.com.

Today is June 8, 2020.  This project was originally written for Python2.
This version runs with Python3.

Dependencies are: pygame and wxpython

Install dependencies like this:
	python3 -m pip install -U pygame --user
	python3 -m pip install -U wxpython --user

Run StepIntoChinese by:
	1. from a terminal (command prompt) changedir into topdir of pkg
	2a. run: python stepintochinese.py
	2b. if using Anaconda python, run with pythonw
